dc_title_s: North part of Ann Arbor and environs: County seat of Washtenaw Co. Mich., Ann Arbor and Pittsfield Twps.
dc_description_s: Shows ward boundaries. North sheet is numbered 10 and 11, south sheet is 14 and 15. 1 map on 2 sheets: col.; 84 x 79 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
